Installations required
1. Install node.js (from web)
2. Install express.js (npm install express)
3. Install CORS (npm install cors)

Deploying a node.js server
1. On terminal, execute command 'npm install'
2. Create a file called server.js
3. Create files called webpage.html and tail.html
4. On terminal, execute code 'node server.js'
5. server.js in now successfully deployed

Using the created APIs
1. APIs shall be called in the html script tag
2. After developing the API code, call the API in a function
3. Return the answers
4. Display the answer in an html div tag using JavaScript